OL,3,CBlind man 'daunted' every time he gets
OL,4,Con a bus
OL,6,FKris Jepson heard how challenging it
OL,7,Fcan be for visually impaired people to
OL,8,Fuse public transport - and what is
OL,9,Fbeing done to improve their experience
OL,11,FA man living with sight loss says he
OL,12,Fis "daunted" every time he gets on a
OL,13,Fbus because he has to rely on members
OL,14,Fof the public to assist him.
OL,16,FPhillip Ward, from Longbenton,
OL,17,FNewcastle, told ITV News Tyne Tees he
OL,18,Fdoes not have the same independence
OL,19,Ffull sighted commuters have due a lack
OL,20,Fof accessibility on the bus networks.
