OL,6,F"It can be very daunting and for some
OL,7,Fpeople it actually is a barrier to
OL,8,Ftrying to use buses at all," he said.
OL,10,F"You're just having to always think
OL,11,Fand be alert and anxiously checking
OL,12,Fwith the members of the public who've
OL,13,Fsaid they're going to help you, to
OL,14,Fmake sure they're still there, or to
OL,15,Foccasionally go to the bus driver to
OL,16,Fmake sure you haven't missed a stop.
OL,18,F"It's not really how people want to
OL,19,Ftravel and no-one else has to
OL,20,Fexperience that."
