OL,6,FTravelling on a bus in Blyth, Phillip
OL,7,Fwas able to experience a journey with
OL,8,Fvisual and audio updates which helped
OL,9,Fhim know where he was on the bus route
OL,10,Fand when to get off.
OL,12,FHe is also partially deaf, so the
OL,13,Faudio visual technology, he said,
OL,14,Freally helps him reclaim his
OL,15,Findependence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
