OL,6,FFrom Monday 8 April, smaller bus and
OL,7,Fcoach operators can apply for a grant
OL,8,Ffrom a #4.65 million pot in order to
OL,9,Finstall the new technology. The grants
OL,10,Fwill help smaller firms come in line
OL,11,Fwith the larger bus operators, like Go
OL,12,FNorth East.
OL,14,FDisability charities have campaigned
OL,15,Ffor the audio visual technology to be
OL,16,Frolled out across the whole transport
OL,17,Fnetwork for more than a decade.
OL,19,Frecently carried out a survey of blind
OL,20,Fcommuters and said the feedback was
OL,21,Fconcerning.
