OL,6,FChris Theobald, from the charity, told
OL,7,FITV News Tyne Tees: "People have
OL,8,Freported how that they'll be let off
OL,9,Fin the dark, in bad weather, in car
OL,10,Fparks in the middle of nowhere, not by
OL,11,Fthe pavement, so they're potentially
OL,12,Fput in danger of oncoming traffic.
OL,14,F"But the big thing is with the
OL,15,Fnegative experiences, people just
OL,16,Fdon't have the confidence to caryy out
OL,17,Fthose journeys independently and just
OL,18,Favoid using buses altogether."
