OL,6,FAround 12 million people in the UK
OL,7,Fhave hearing loss and up to two
OL,8,Fmillion live with sight loss, so
OL,9,Finstalling the sensory updates on all
OL,10,Fbuses by October 2026 will benefit
OL,11,Fmany of those commuters.
OL,13,FGo North East already has the tech
OL,14,Finstalled.
