OL,6,FBen Maxfield, from the bus company,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We programme into a system all
OL,8,Fof the stops along a route and the
OL,9,Fspeakers then announce those stops as
OL,10,Fand when the buses are approaching
OL,11,Fthem. In all honesty, it provides a
OL,12,Freally great addition to our
OL,13,Faccessibility."
