OL,6,FTransport Minister, Guy Opperman, told
OL,7,FITV News: "This grant funding for the
OL,8,Fsmaller operators is our way of
OL,9,Fhelping them get this over the line,
OL,10,Fso that the bus should be accessible
OL,11,Ffor everyone and, most importantly,
OL,12,Feverybody should have the ability to
OL,13,Fget any bus and it is accessible."
